sequenceDiagram
    participant ui as 前端UI
    participant api as API网关
    participant queue as 任务队列
    participant engine as 计算引擎
    participant store as 内存状态存储

    ui->>api: POST /analysis/jobs (参数)
    api->>queue: 入队(job)
    queue-->>api: task_id
    api-->>ui: 202 + task_id

    loop 每500ms（非阻塞轮询）
        ui->>api: GET /analysis/jobs/{task_id}/status
        api->>store: 读取 status/progress
        store-->>api: {status:"running", progress:45%}
        api-->>ui: 返回状态
    end

    queue->>engine: 分发(task_id)
    engine->>store: 更新进度
    engine-->>store: 写入 done + resultIndex

    ui->>api: GET /analysis/jobs/{task_id}/result
    api->>store: 读取 resultIndex
    store-->>api: 返回结果数据
    api-->>ui: 紧凑结果载荷
    ui->>ui: 重建渲染图层
